                  |   – Nearly 300,000 people have benefited from our knowledge and integrity in research communication.
          .row
            .col.col-lg-6
              .col.col-lg-6
              .row
                .col-1
                  <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
                p.whywe__content-item.col
