                  |   – Our language and design/production skills combine to produce powerful, effective communication.
            .col.col-lg-6
              .row
                .col-1
                  <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
                p.whywe__content-item.col
                  b Global reach
                  |  – We work with people, institutions and companies from all over the world - easily, quickly and very effectively.
        .row
          button.weare__button(type="button" class="btn btn-warning") Read more
